<item>
            <title>[LU-8289] add ll_decode_linkea tool</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8289</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A MDT recovered by fsck might contain some files under lost+found&lt;br/&gt;
directory of ldiskfs. And in order to get the right path to move&lt;br/&gt;
them to, the xattr of trusted.link could be used to extract the&lt;br/&gt;
parent FIDs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This path adds an new tool ll_decode_linkea to dump the parent FIDs&lt;br/&gt;
of a file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
